            <title>[SHINDIG-971] JsonRpcServlet should set content type to json in all cases, including gets and error cases. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHINDIG-971</link>
                <project id="12310741" key="SHINDIG">Shindig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the JsonRpcServlet only sets the content type in the case of a properly formed post request. It should also do it in the sendError case, and in the GET request method case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
